      "text": "Schee irr Ichkaba Raddi:\nJahseps ſeptinpadeſinitis Gad-\nus wezz buhdams / gannija ar\nfaueem Brahteem tahs Anis /\nm tas Puifens bija ar Billas\nDchleem / un ar Silpas fawa\nTehwa Seewu Dehleem/un Jah-\neps neffe wiſfu winno niknu Sla-\nvn winno Tehwain preekſchâ.\n"
