    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Iſrâêls mihleja Jahsepu\npahr wiſſeem faueem Behrneem /\nio tas bija winnam Wezzumâ\nosimnis / un wiꞥſch darrija tam\nraibus Swahrkus.\n"
