    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Brahti redſeja/\nta winno Tehws to / pahr wi-\nfeem faueem Brahteem mihleja/\nn eenihdeja to/ un ne warreja to\ntteerigt bildinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad arri ſapnoja Jahse-\npam kahds Sapnis / un tas pa-\nſazzija to faueem Brahteem /\ntad eenihdeja winni to wehl wai-\nraſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch ſazzija uhs teem:\nKlaufajt jelle fcho Sapni / fo es\neſmu redſejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un redſi/ mehs fehjam Kuḥ-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſazztja winna Brah-\nus to : Ar tu waldidams pal-\nmuns waldfizi? ar tu pahr mum-\ntahdu Warru turreſti ? un eenil-\ndeja to wehl wairak/ pehz winna\nSapneem/un pehz winnaStol-\nsteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tam ſapnoja wehl zitt\nSapnis / un taſteize to faueei-\nBrahteem/ un ſazzija : Reds/\neſmu wehl zittu Sapni redſeje-\nun redſi/ ta Saule/ un tas Mel-\nnes/ un weenpadeſinitis Swaig-\nnes paklannijahs preekſch manni-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥſch to fauea-\nTehwam un faueem Brahte-\nhuddinaja / apſauze to win-\nTehws / un ſazzija us to : Ka-\ntas par Sapni / fo tu effi v-\ndſejs ? Wojes/ un taiwa Maht-\nun tawi Brahti/ pateefi nahſti-\nflannidamees preekſch tevis p-\nSemines?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna Brahti ska-\nto / bet winna Tehws pature-\nscho Wahrdiu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna Brahti ga-\nfata Tehwa Lohpus ganni-\nSikema / tad ſazzija Iſraê-\nuhs Jahsepu.\n"
    },
